programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Detective Dee and Nine-storey Demon Building
programme.desc: A series of strange incidents happen at the Tang’s demon building but Detective Dee finds no clue. Dee finds the master of the family suspicious when he speaks with him, and when the eldest daughter Miss Tang secretly informs Dee about Mr Tang’s strange behavior and the fact that she is kept under surveillance, Dee vows to unveil the truth.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the police’s only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Chungking Express
programme.desc: Two Hong Kong urban love stories depicting two Hong Kong policemen, both jilted by ex-lovers and falling in love again. One falls for a mysterious female underworld figure while the other is in love with a beautiful and witty server at a fast food restaurant he frequents.

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sect’s Zhang Chui Shan’s son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriend’s wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge – will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kong’s Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Chang’s first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunt’s puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: Grandmaster, The
programme.desc: Directed by the acclaimed filmmaker Wong Kar Wai, this epic action feature begins in Foshan when Ip Man, the martial arts master from the south, takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tian’s daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond…

programme.title: Behind the Yellow Line
programme.desc: A fresh graduate, Paul, strikes up an acquaintance with a pretty young girl, Monica, on the metro. Monica is involved in a love affair with a married man while Paul is also pursued by a rich girl. When Paul vows his true love for Monica, she suggests playing hide-and-seek with him in the metro to decide if they are fated to be together.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his family’s expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his family’s reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Echoes of the Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killer’s mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened…

programme.title: Home Sweet Home
programme.desc: A school bus accident kills almost everyone on board. The bus driver got injured and partially lost his memory while rescuing one of the boys. To thank the driver, the boy’s dad, Wang, brings him to live with the family in their basement. However, the driver soon discovers strange behaviours from the Wang’s which seem to be related to the accident.

programme.title: Twilight of the Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Young Chan Lok Kwun accidentally stumbles into the Kowloon Walled City while fleeing, subsequently finding purpose amid chaos and gaining wisdom. Bonding with Shin, Twelfth Master and AV, they unite under Tornado's leadership to defend against the villain, Mr Big's assaults, and pledge to protect the safe haven of the Walled City together.

programme.title: Painted Faces
programme.desc: This is based on the real-life story of Master Yu Jim Yuen who strives to run his academy in the 1960s, even as the opera culture is declining. Three young men, Sammo Hung, Jackie Chan and Yuen Biao, are determined to train under Master Yu and undergo extremely tough training before they become three of Hong Kong’s biggest stars

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his father’s death…

programme.title: The Lady Iron Chef
programme.desc: Beer girl and part-time model Ceci has terrible cooking skills. Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown…

programme.title: Don't Forget I Love You
programme.desc: Lu Yao suffers from amnesia and forgets about everything that happens yesterday when he wakes up the next day. When Lu Yao meets psychotherapist Xing Yue, they fall in love despite knowing they have no future together, and are determined to love each other no matter what happens...

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Founded in the 70s, Hong Kong’s ICAC is committed to fight corruption in the police force. Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end. Where the wind blows, Hong Kong is no longer what it used to be!

programme.title: Fallen Angels

Karen Mok won Best Supporting Actress in the 15th Hong Kong Film Awards for her remarkable role as a broken-hearted party girl.

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness…

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartel’s turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brother’s hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: As It Burns
programme.desc: Detective Wei investigates the death of Yan Zhen in an explosion which seems more than an accident to him. Wei then finds out that Yan Zhen looks a lot like Yin, the girlfriend of Yan Zhen’s childhood friend Lu, and uncovers a tangled web of deceit leading to surprising revelations when he merges details from the past and the present.

programme.title: The Captain
programme.desc: The movie is based on a real incident of Sichuan Airlines Flight 8633 on 14 May 2018. When the cockpit windshield shatters after takeoff, the Captain manages to land the airplane safely with his level-headed swift actions and sheer determination. This is lauded as a miracle in airline history.

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kit’s master, Debo.

programme.title: The Locksmith
programme.desc: Locksmith Master Shan suffers from dementia and passes on his skills to Hao Ren, who surpasses him. Detective Liu often seeks Hao Ren's help and they become good friends. When Hao Ren reunites with an old friend one day, he accidentally unfolds the truth behind Shan's wife's disappearance, leading to a chain of mysterious events.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Detective Dee and Nine-storey Demon Building
programme.desc: A series of strange incidents happen at the Tang’s demon building but Detective Dee finds no clue. Dee finds the master of the family suspicious when he speaks with him, and when the eldest daughter Miss Tang secretly informs Dee about Mr Tang’s strange behavior and the fact that she is kept under surveillance, Dee vows to unveil the truth.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the police’s only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Chungking Express
programme.desc: Two Hong Kong urban love stories depicting two Hong Kong policemen, both jilted by ex-lovers and falling in love again. One falls for a mysterious female underworld figure while the other is in love with a beautiful and witty server at a fast food restaurant he frequents.

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sect’s Zhang Chui Shan’s son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriend’s wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge – will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kong’s Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Chang’s first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunt’s puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: Grandmaster, The
programme.desc: Directed by the acclaimed filmmaker Wong Kar Wai, this epic action feature begins in Foshan when Ip Man, the martial arts master from the south, takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tian’s daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond…

programme.title: Behind the Yellow Line
programme.desc: A fresh graduate, Paul, strikes up an acquaintance with a pretty young girl, Monica, on the metro. Monica is involved in a love affair with a married man while Paul is also pursued by a rich girl. When Paul vows his true love for Monica, she suggests playing hide-and-seek with him in the metro to decide if they are fated to be together.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his family’s expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his family’s reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Echoes of the Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killer’s mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened…

programme.title: Home Sweet Home
programme.desc: A school bus accident kills almost everyone on board. The bus driver got injured and partially lost his memory while rescuing one of the boys. To thank the driver, the boy’s dad, Wang, brings him to live with the family in their basement. However, the driver soon discovers strange behaviours from the Wang’s which seem to be related to the accident.

programme.title: Twilight of the Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Young Chan Lok Kwun accidentally stumbles into the Kowloon Walled City while fleeing, subsequently finding purpose amid chaos and gaining wisdom. Bonding with Shin, Twelfth Master and AV, they unite under Tornado's leadership to defend against the villain, Mr Big's assaults, and pledge to protect the safe haven of the Walled City together.

programme.title: Painted Faces
programme.desc: This is based on the real-life story of Master Yu Jim Yuen who strives to run his academy in the 1960s, even as the opera culture is declining. Three young men, Sammo Hung, Jackie Chan and Yuen Biao, are determined to train under Master Yu and undergo extremely tough training before they become three of Hong Kong’s biggest stars

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his father’s death…

programme.title: The Lady Iron Chef
programme.desc: Beer girl and part-time model Ceci has terrible cooking skills. Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown…

programme.title: Don't Forget I Love You
programme.desc: Lu Yao suffers from amnesia and forgets about everything that happens yesterday when he wakes up the next day. When Lu Yao meets psychotherapist Xing Yue, they fall in love despite knowing they have no future together, and are determined to love each other no matter what happens...

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Founded in the 70s, Hong Kong’s ICAC is committed to fight corruption in the police force. Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end. Where the wind blows, Hong Kong is no longer what it used to be!

programme.desc: Kisah tentang arwah gentayangan, pocong dan kuntilanak yang kerap meneror warga kampung. Fenomena ini disiasati Acong. programme.title: Menerjang Badai
programme.desc: Merupakan kelanjutan dari film "Orang-orang di Atas Angin". Di film ini Bastian berkisah mundur mengenai masa lalu ia dan Zainal pada anak-anaknya. Zainal, anak seorang pemilik perusahaan diusir ayahnya saat hendak menolong Bastian, anak seorang narapidana. Mereka berjuang bersama sampai akhirnya terlibat dalam komplotan penyelundup emas. Siapa menyelamatkan siapa menjadi bahan pertengkaran juga pada saat cerita berakhir di masa kini.

programme.title: Sunan Gunung Jati
programme.desc: Kisah Sunan Gunung Jati yang berusaha menyiarkan Islam di Cirebon dengan menunjukkan kemampuannya agar orang percaya akan adanya Allah. Ia juga berusaha melawan kedigdayaan raja Cakraningrat dengan tidak mau membayar upeti lagi. Karena Cakraningrat sulit ditaklukan dalam perang, maka ia menyuruh anaknya untuk mencuri jimat Cakraningrat.

programme.title: Hantu Juga Selfie
programme.desc: Helsi meninggal karena selfie, ia meneror temen-teman semasa hidupnya ketika mereka melakukan selfie. Hal ini membuat teman-temanya ketakutan, apa lagi bukan hanya sosok Helsi yang ada dalam foto namun hantu-hantu kocak lainya juga ada saat mereka berlibur di sebuah pulau.

programme.title: Mencari Hilal
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Mahmud yang selalu ingin mengajarkan bahwa Islam itu adalah agama untuk semua persoalan hidup. Dalam perjalannya mencari hilal dengan caranya yang sederhana tanpa menelan biaya sampai milyaran rupiah yang selama ini dilakukan oleh pemerintah, langkahnya terhalang dengan anaknya bernama Heli. Heli selau melontarkan pikiran liberalnya hingga membuat Mahmud gerah.

programme.desc: Tiga cewek cantik dan bokek mau tidak mau harus jumpalitan, putar otak, dan baca mantra buat mengusir preman yang mau menggusur rumah kost mereka. Sambil rebutan cowok, pula!

programme.title: Dunia Mereka
programme.desc: Film ini menceritakan tentang sebuah band yang terdiri dari beberapa orang yang mempertemukan mereka karena selera musik yang sama. Namun dalam perjalanan mereka, berbagai masalah pun berdatangan.

programme.title: Roy Kiyoshi (The Untold Story)
programme.desc: Roy, yang punya kemampuan berinteraksi dengan makhluk gaib sangat frustrasi ketika Rani adiknya diculik setan. Roy merasa gagal melindungi adiknya. Tiga tahun kemudian, Sheila, pekerja LSM yang peduli dalam penanggulangan anak hilang diteror setan ketika sedang menangani kasus anak hilang secara misterius. Sheila sangat yakin bahwa kemunculan setan ini ada hubungannya dengan kasus yang sedang ditanganinya.

programme.title: Love You Love You Not
programme.desc: Sebuah komedi romantis tentang Amira, guru les Bahasa Inggris, dan Juki, pemuda Betawi yang geragasan. Semua dimulai saat Suchin, gadis Thailand yang juga pacar Juki, meminta bantuan Amira, guru les Bahasa Inggrisnya, untuk menyampaikan ke Juki bahwa mereka putus karena ia mendapat pekerjaan di Amerika. Selama ini ia dan Juki pacaran dan berkomunikasi lewat bahasa gerak gerik. Begitu Amira menyampaikan pesan Suchin, Juki tidak terima dan memaksa Amira mengajarinya Bahasa Inggris, agar bisa menyusul Suchin. Karena takut dengan Juki, Amira mengajar privat Juki. Di saat yang sama, pemuda lain, Taufan, mendekati Amira.

programme.title: Pohon Keramat
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang keluarga yang diteror oleh hantu pohon besar yang ada di depan rumah baru mereka. Keganjilan demi keganjilan terus berlanjut dan selalu mengintai keluarga tersebut.

programme.title: Semua Karena Ginah
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang seorang penjual jamu gendong yang banyak diidolai pria tiba-tiba menjadi terkenal karena menjadi model sebuah perusahaan jamu. Namun bukan kebahagiaan yang ia dapat, malah keresahan.

programme.title: Skandal
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang seorang wanita yang selingkuh dengan kekasih lamanya karena merasa jenuh dengan kehidupan rumah tangganya. Dengan sifat posesif yang dimiliki kekasih lamanya, teror demi teror mulai diterima wanita itu dan keluarganya.

programme.title: Kesurupan Jumat Kliwon
programme.desc: Menceritakan keempat pemuda yang memutuskan untuk bunuh diri karena berbagai masalah. Sebelum bunuh diri, mereka berlibur di rumah tua dekat pantai, yang dimana rumah itu terkenal angker. Terror kepada mereka pun terus berlanjut dihari pertama yaitu malam jumat kliwon.

programme.title: Tabah Sampai Akhir
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang tiga anak yatim piatu yang berangkat ke Jakarta untuk mencari pamannya. Ternyata Jakarta memang keras, mereka mengalami kesulitan-kesulitan, seperti ditipu. Lalu mereka ditolong Hadi hingga bisa menemukan pamannya. Tetapi kemudian mereka mengalami kecelakaan yanga membuat pamannya tewas, sementara mereka bertiga jadi cacat seperti gagu, pincang dan buta. Setelah menjadi gelandangan, mereka masing2 diadopsi hingga bisa menjadi Pesilat, dokter dan pianis.

programme.title: Bidadari Pulau Hantu
programme.desc: Evan dan Gesti melakukan pemotretan pre-wedding di pulau yang dikenal sebagai pulau hantu. Pulau ini terkenal dengan sosok hantu perempuan yang membawa celurit dan menggunakan gaun pengantin. Pasangan ini mengajak Remon seorang fotografer, Remi, pria penata rias kemayu, Vidi, sepupu Gesti, dan Tilda. Di hari pertama pemotretan, hantu perempuan bergaun pengantin sudah menteror rombongan Evan dan Gesti

programme.title: Ganesha
programme.desc: Ganesha, pemuda daerah yang mencoba mengadu nasib di kota, karena atas pengaruh temannya. Pada saat perjalanan, ia berhasil menggagalkan aksi pembajakan di bis yang ia tumpangi. Sang supir pun berterima kasih kepadanya dan mengangkatnya anak.

programme.title: Menggapai Matahari
programme.desc: Mobil yang dikendarai Tika, kekasih Rhoma Irama, menabrak Selvy hingga tewas. Rhoma Irama mengaku sebagai pengendara mobil tersebut untuk meyelamatkan kekasihnya dari penjara. Indra, kekasih Selvy, berusaha merebut Tika dari Rhoma Irama, sedangkan Beny Compo, kakak Selvy, berusaha menghancurkan karir musik Rhoma Irama sebagai pelampiasan dendam

programme.title: Bing Slamet Dukun Palsu
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Bing Slamet yang menjalani profesi sebagai dukun palsu dan telah menipu banyak orang termasuk Ateng dan Iskak. Karena Merasa ditipu, orang-orang yang pernah menjadi korban dukun tersebut bermaksud menangkapnya, tapi keduluan polisi.

programme.title: Senggol Bacok
programme.desc: Galang tempramental & tidak pernah takut apapun, namun ia harus mengendalikan emosinya untuk dapat memenangkan hati sang cewek idaman.

Menceritakan tentang rumah yang baru ditempati oleh Kevin dan Nayla. Mereka bertetangga oleh Julian, Dita dan anaknya Lila. Namun ternyata rumah mereka berpenghuni mahluk halus yang selalu meneror keluarga-nya. Kejadian fatal yang membuat Nayla membunuh Kevin adalah ketika Nayla diperkosa oleh mahluk halus yang menyerupai Kevin hingga Nayla hamil.

programme.title: Cinta Tapi Beda

programme.title: Si Manis Jembatan Ancol

Hadirnya sosok Yudha mampu membuat Maryam menemukan ketenangan. Namun, sebuah kejadian tragis harus menimpanya. Setelah itu legenda menyeramkan mulai tersebar.

programme.title: Soap: Il Paradiso delle Signore 8 Daily
Jagoan Silat
programme.desc: Serial Indonesia yang bercerita mengenai kehidupan seorang anak laki-laki bernama Toyib yang ingin menjadi seorang Jagoan Silat. Namun, impiannya ditentang oleh ibunya dikarenakan ayahnya Toyib yang seorang jagoan silat dianggap meninggal dengan tidak wajar. Walaupun demikian, tidak membuat Toyib mengurungkan impiannya untuk menjadi seorang Jagoan Silat. Banyak drama, pesan moral serta hikmah yang dapat diambil pada program ini.

programme.title: Terang Kasih
programme.desc: Siraman rohani Kristen yang berkaitan dengan kehidupan untuk mendekatkan diri kepada Tuhan Yesus Kristus. Program ini akan dibagi menjadi beberapa bagian, antara lain kesaksian, renungan, serta konseling yang akan dipandu oleh dua orang host

programme.title: STB (Sangat Tidak Biasa)
programme.desc: Program ini menghadirkan kompilasi informasi berbagai macam issue dan topik yang akan dibahas dari berbagai sisi dan dipaparkan oleh penyulih suara.

programme.title: Top Trending
programme.desc: Program TV berjenis informasi documentary yang mengangkat suatu hal atau issue yang sedang trending, dibahas dari berbagai sisi, dan dipaparkan oleh VO ( Voice Over ). Setiap segmen menampilkan fakta terunik, asal usul, fenomena yang trending.

programme.title: Omar & Hana
programme.desc: Omar & Hana adalah serial animasi anak bergenre hiburan pendidikan dengan tokoh kakak-beradik yang bahagia, ingin tahu, dan penuh kasih. Mereka menarik teman-teman di seluruh dunia ke dunia mereka yang menakjubkan.

programme.title: Mina Mila
programme.desc: Serial animasi religi islami yang menceritakan kehidupan sehari-hari antara dua anak kembar Mina dan Mila. Program ini akan mengajak penonton untuk belajar, melakukan hal-hal baik, bermain, serta bernyanyi bersama.

programme.title: Ibra Berkisah
programme.desc: Ibrahim atau Ibra adalah murid pesantren yang santun dan selalu mengajak teman-temannya untuk meneladani Nabi Muhammad SAW, dia pun sejak kecil sudah tinggal di pesantren. Ibra memiliki teman bernama Tokek dan Hoho. Tokek adalah anak yang lucu dan periang, sedangkan Hoho adalah seorang anak Jakarta yang dilahirkan dari keluarga kaya raya, sifatnya manja dan tidak mengerti sama sekali tentang islam. Selama di Pesantren, Hoho sekamar dengan Ibra yang mana di perkenalan awal mereka, Hoho menganggap remeh Ibra yang dia anggap sebagai anak kampung. Tapi ternyata dari Ibra lah Hoho banyak mendapatkan pelajaran hidup dan kisah-kisah teladan Nabi Muhammad Shalallahu Alaihi Wassalam.

programme.title: Riko The Series
programme.desc: Animasi lokal yang mengangkat keseharian seorang anak bernama Riko bersama sahabat robotnya, Q110 untuk menemukan dan mempelajari hal-hal baru disekitarnya. Q110 bertugas menjelaskan kepada Riko hal-hal baru yang mereka temukan. Berkat Q110, Riko mempelajari banyak pengetahuan soal ilmuan-ilmuan muslim dari penjuru dunia, kekuasaan Allah sang Maha Pencipta, dan tentunya banyak hal lainya.

programme.title: Santri Boy
programme.desc: Sebuah serial animasi Indonesia yang diadaptasi dari tiga santri laki-laki bernama Badrun, Sinyo, dan Goni yang dihadapkan pada permasalahan sehari-hari di pesantren, dikemas apik dengan bahasa sehari-hari yang merakyat. Aksi kocak ketiga tokoh kartun tersebut memiliki ciri khas masing-masing, yang sesuai dengan budaya Indonesia dan dapat menghibur.

programme.title: Adit Sopo Jarwo
programme.desc: Animasi Indonesia, berisikan kisah kehidupan sehari-hari masyarakat Indonesia yang dipenuhi dengan pengetahuan, kelucuan, kisah persahabatan, serta nilai persatuan, kesatuan, dan kebudayaan. Tokoh dalam cerita ini diantaranya Adit (tokoh utama, seorang anak laki-laki), Adelya (adik Adit), teman-teman Adit yakni Dennis, Mitha, dan Devi. Mereka harus berhadapan dengan duo orang dewasa (Sopo & Jarwo) yang selalu mencari celah untuk mendapat keuntungan tanpa usaha. Perbedaan paham atau cara pandang merupakan bumbu utama yang memicu “perseteruan” dan "kelucuan". Beruntung di antara mereka ada H. Udin, ketua RW bijaksana yang selalu menjadi penengah dan memberikan petuah bijak yang disampaikan dengan ringan serta lugas sehingga mampu mengembalikan suasana gaduh menjadi teduh.

programme.title: Super Wings
programme.desc: Jett dan teman-temannya, Super Wings, terus menghadapi tantangan baru di setiap pengiriman. Mereka harus bekerja sama untuk memecahkan masalah dengan menggunakan keahlian unik mereka. Pada musim ini Jett memiliki perubahan pada tenaga supernya yaitu menggunakan mesin listrik! Memiliki desain futuristic dan lebih ramping dari sebelumnya, mereka dibuat seperti itu agar sesuai dengan konsep listrik baru dan mereka juga menyambut energi terbaru yang bersih dan ramah lingkungan.

programme.title: PJ Masks
programme.desc: Serial animasi ini berkisah tentang tiga anak normal yang berkegiatan pada siang hari. Namun pada malam hari, mereka akan menjadi pahlawan yang menggunakan topeng. Biasanya, masalah itu terjadi pada siang hari saat mereka sekolah. Dan tugas mereka, menyelesaikan masalah itu pada malam harinya. Akan ada banyak ide dan strategi yang mereka gunakan dalam memecahkan masalah. Mereka sangat mengenali kekuatan dan kelemahan masing-masing. Mereka memutuskan beraksi pada malam hari karena menganggap waktu tidur merupakan waktu yang tepat untuk memerangi kejahatan.

programme.title: Keluarga Ceria (Kece)
programme.desc: KECE (Keluarga Ceria) merupakan program variety show yang menampilkan beberapa permainan yang terdiri dari 3 grup yang mana pesertanya adalah ibu-ibu dan anak-anak, setiap permainan akan dipandu oleh Host yang pastinya ceria dan seru. Tidak hanya permainan, pada program ini juga menampilkan pertunjukan seperti menyanyi, menari, dll

programme.title: Boboiboy
programme.desc: Sebuah program animasi yang mengisahkan Boboiboy dan teman-temannya yakni Gopal, Ying, dan Yaya yang masing-masing memiliki kekuatan super. Dengan kekuatan yang dimiliki mereka mencegah Adu Du mencuri biji kakao Tok Aba yang digunakan sebagai sumber energi. Selain itu, Boboiboy dan teman-temannya menjadi pahlawan super dalam menumpas kejahatan dan menjaga kedamaian Bumi.

programme.title: Beyblade X
programme.desc: Beyblade X mengikuti kisah Robin Kazami, seorang Blader muda yang ditinggalkan timnya setelah kekalahan telak. Dia kemudian bertemu dengan Jaxon Cross, mantan juara Beyblade, dan mereka berdua membentuk tim baru bernama Tim Persona. Bersama dengan anggota ketiga tim, Multi Nana-iro, mereka bercita-cita untuk mencapai puncak liga Beyblade X.

programme.title: Ejen Ali
programme.desc: Serial animasi dengan tokoh utama bernama Ali yang tidak sengaja menjadi agen Meta Advance Tactical Agency (MATA). Ali membuktikan diri bahwa Ia mampu menjadi agen MATA dan mengalahkan musuh bersama Alicia dan Paman bakar

programme.title: Boboiboy Galaxy 2
programme.desc: Boboiboy Galaxy Sori merupakan sekuel lanjutan dari Boboiboy The Movie 2, dimana setelah Boboiboy berhasil mengalahkan Retak'ka, penguasa elemen yang kejam. Boboiboy dan teman-temannya pulang ke Bumi untuk menunggu tugas selanjutnya. Tanpa diduga, seorang musuh lama muncul kembali dengan rencana jahat yang baru. Boboiboy harus mempelajari kekuatan elemen tahap ketiga di Planet Rimbara, bekas jajahan King Balakung, pemilik asli Kuasa Elemental Balak yang tewas ditangan Retak'ka.

programme.title: Adit Sopo Jarwo
programme.desc: Animasi Indonesia, berisikan kisah kehidupan sehari-hari masyarakat Indonesia yang dipenuhi dengan pengetahuan, kelucuan, kisah persahabatan, serta nilai persatuan, kesatuan, dan kebudayaan. programme.title: Boboiboy Galaxy 2
programme.desc: Busur Windara terjadi di Kerajaan Planet Windara. Seorang Elemental Master Kuputeri yang mungkin sudah mati kembali dan menuntut Elemental Anginnya kembali ke bahwa dia dapat menyelamatkan planetnya yang telah jatuh di bawah kekuasaan seorang tiran. BoBoiBoy dan teman-temannya memutuskan untuk membantu putri yang jatuh untuk merebut kembali tahtanya dan menyelamatkan rakyatnya. Akan melemparkan serangkaian tantangan dan pertempuran, busur penuh aksi ini diakhiri dengan debut elemen lapis ketiga pertama BoBoiBoy, BoBoiBoy Tempest. Busur ini menyoroti nasib Elemental Master asli lainnya, bersama dengan akibat yang diciptakan oleh keserakahan dan perbuatan jahat Retak'ka.

programme.title: Mechamato
programme.desc: Sebuah program animasi yang menceritakan seorang anak laki-laki bernama Amato dalam menemukan sebuah pesawat ruang angkasa penjara berisi robot-robot jahat yang telah jatuh ke bumi. Salah satu robot tersebut adalah MechaBot yang memiliki kemampuan untuk mengubah objek sehari-hari menjadi perangkat berteknologi tinggi. Amato berhasil menginovasi MechaBot menjadi master MechaBot. Sejak itu, MechaBot dan Amato mulai bekerja sama untuk menemukan dan menangkap robot jahat.

Mereka memutuskan beraksi pada malam hari karena menganggap waktu tidur merupakan waktu yang tepat untuk memerangi kejahatan.

programme.title: Boboiboy Galaxy 2
programme.desc: Busur Windara terjadi di Kerajaan Planet Windara. Seorang Elemental Master Kuputeri yang mungkin sudah mati kembali dan menuntut Elemental Anginnya kembali ke bahwa dia dapat menyelamatkan planetnya yang telah jatuh di bawah kekuasaan seorang tiran. BoBoiBoy dan teman-temannya memutuskan untuk membantu putri yang jatuh untuk merebut kembali tahtanya dan menyelamatkan rakyatnya. Akan melemparkan serangkaian tantangan dan pertempuran, busur penuh aksi ini diakhiri dengan debut elemen lapis ketiga pertama BoBoiBoy, BoBoiBoy Tempest. Busur ini menyoroti nasib Elemental Master asli lainnya, bersama dengan akibat yang diciptakan oleh keserakahan dan perbuatan jahat Retak'ka.

programme.title: This Is Where I Leave You
programme.desc: When their father passes away, four grown siblings (Jason Bateman, Tina Fey, Adam Driver, Corey Stoll), bruised and banged up by their respective adult lives, are forced to return to their childhood home and live under the same roof together for a week, along with their over-sharing mother (Jane Fonda) and an assortment of spouses, exes and might-have-beens. Confronting their history and the frayed states of their relationships among the people who know and love them best, they ultimately reconnect in hysterical and emotionally affecting ways amid the chaos, humor, heartache and redemption that only families can provide-- driving us insane even as they remind us of our truest, and often best, selves. Comedy director Shawn Levy (Date Night)helms the hilarious script by Jonathan Tropper based on his own best-selling novel.

Hero is a word we often hear in the world of sports, but heroism is not always about achievements on the field of play. 42 tells the story of two men -- the great Jackie Robinson (Chadwick Boseman) and the legendary Brooklyn Dodgers manager Branch Rickey (Harrison Ford) -- whose brave stand against prejudice forever changed the world by changing the game of baseball. In 1946, Rickey signed Robinson to the team, breaking Major League Baseball's infamous color line. Facing racism from every side, Robinson demonstrated tremendous courage by letting his talent on the field do the talking -- ultimately winning over fans and his teammates, and paving the way for others to follow.
